<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5184131>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Anterior end of Bhawania pottsiana (mCT-00084), imaged through micro-CT and rendered in 3D. (a) dorsal view; (b) dorsal view, virtually dissected to expose pharyngeal structures; (c) lateral view, semi-transparent rendering to show position of jaws; (d) lateral view, virtually dissected to expose pharyngeal structures." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5184131/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5184133>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Jaws of Bhawania spp., imaged through micro-CT. (a) B. amboinensis (mCT-00100), lateral view; (b) B. cf riveti (mCT-00037), posterior view; (c) B. amboinensis (mCT-00100), dorsal view and cross sections through the jaw along its length." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5184133/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

